{"type": "article", "id": 8915, "title": "如果你也想在朋友圈卖韩国面膜", "description": "先看看这14个韩国彩妆网站吧。", "date": "2015-04-27T08:18:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 620, "name": "韩国"}, {"id": 9406, "name": "K beauty"}, {"id": 2593, "name": "美妆"}, {"id": 6283, "name": "网站"}], "category": 19, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 301, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141440vTeqsZalEGIB15pc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t韩国的流行文化叫 K-POP，韩国的美妆行业叫 K-beauty，“韩国的”汤唯叫 K-wife（嗯，瞎编的）。总之韩国在综艺、美妆、造星等领域确实有牛叉的地方。不信看看你朋友圈里卖的面膜，有一半都写着“韩国制造”。不论你只是一个韩式美妆的爱好者，还是想了解一下韩国的美妆行业，都可以先浏览<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/04/best-korean-beauty-blogs-websites\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">下面这 14 个网站</a>，不懂韩文没关系，因为它们都是英文的。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tREDDIT\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141433J0lyhZOGoW94eLmq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t <a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/AsianBeauty/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\">AsianBeauty</a> ，这是一个信息聚合类网站，在这里几乎能找到与韩国彩妆有关的一切东西。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tFANSERVICED-B\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141434tj7qVCIhm6DseyBA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<a href=\"%E3%80%81http://www.fanserviced-b.com\" target=\"_blank\">这家网站</a>是一个名叫 Tracy 的美国女孩创办的，她是个韩国化妆品的狂热爱好者，测试了多种韩国祛痘产品。如果你恰巧在纽约，还可以按照她给出的示意图，在纽约买到便宜的韩国化妆品……\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tTHE BEAUTY WOLF \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141434vG0ZykfYzFrbJLMC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">博主是加拿大人 </span><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">Coco Park</span><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">，她为多款产品写了<a href=\"http://www.thebeautywolf.com/\" target=\"_blank\">试用感受</a>，每款产品下面还附有多个购买地址。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tTHE WANDERLUST PROJECT \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141435Gy0TKJQ78VpuwIRr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://thewanderlustproject.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Wanderlust Project </a>的博主是 Shelly，她是一个曾在韩国教书的美国女孩，现在人在越南。她也晒出了不少她感兴趣的韩国美妆，另外，她对颜色搭配很有自己的看法。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tSNOW WHITE AND THE ASIAN PEAR \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141435u6qxGZVTmOiSg7e2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\"></span><a href=\"http://snowwhiteandthepear.blogspot.com/\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;white-space:normal;\">Snow White</a><span style=\"white-space:normal;\"> </span><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">是</span><span style=\"white-space:normal;\">内容排列得井井有条的一个。博主保持着有规律的更新，还给</span>油性皮肤女生提出了很多小建议。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tFIFTY SHADES OF SNAIL \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141435zy5T7musBnrKvq4C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t博主称自己为“<a href=\"http://fiftyshadesofsnail.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Crazy Snail Lady</a>”，她今年三十五岁了，是一个 K-beauty 的狂热爱好者。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tMEMORABLE DAYS \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060614143619NWGajfgk6upOHo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://www.memorable-days.net/\">Memorable\r\nDays</a> </span>是一个集合了时尚内容和美食菜谱的博客，站内多是一些主流的韩国化妆品牌。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:tablet-gothic-condensed, sans-serif;font-size:2.6rem;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;color:#333333;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n\tADOREDEE \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141436uSVgGZYKpUzmBNr6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://adoredee.com/\">Adoredee</a> </span>网站适合深肤色的女生。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tSUN HYE MI  \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141437hzD3NeFauHXLOcZo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.596875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t在十四个网站中，这是<a href=\"http://sunhyemi.com/\" target=\"_blank\">最专业的一个</a>。产品规格和试用感受都标注得很清晰。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tMIZUCHAN \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141437YLqjFPHGQ5h3RUWw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这家网站是一个马来西亚女孩开的，专注于彩妆。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tGLOW RECIPE \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141438tpeP8c7xBJVlkC6i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://blog.glowrecipe.com/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:0px;transition:all 0.25s ease;-webkit-transition:all 0.25s ease;line-height:1.6em;background-image:linear-gradient(transparent 49%, #4F95FC 50%);background-size:2px;text-shadow:white -2px 0px, white -1px 0px, white 1px 0px, #FFFFFF 2px 0px;white-space:normal;background-position:0px 90%;background-repeat:repeat no-repeat;\">Glow Recipe</a> 这是一个电商网站，由两个韩国人创建，网站的特色是商品分类很详细。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tSOKOGLAM \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141438QjvKwbXNaLUAWoHE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://sokoglam.com/blogs/news\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:0px;transition:all 0.25s ease;-webkit-transition:all 0.25s ease;line-height:1.6em;background-image:linear-gradient(transparent 49%, #4F95FC 50%);background-size:2px;text-shadow:white -2px 0px, white -1px 0px, white 1px 0px, #FFFFFF 2px 0px;white-space:normal;background-position:0px 90%;background-repeat:repeat no-repeat;\">SokoGlam</a>  的创始人是一个热衷于环球旅行的女孩，她在自己的网站里即时更新旅行日记和产品试用清单。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tPEACH AND LILY \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141439Q3okDnvA5SZbIHTi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://blog.peachandlily.com/\">Peach and\r\nLily</a> </span>的主人是一个经验丰富又老练的业内人士，她访问了许多温泉主和韩国的皮肤科医生，并将文章贴到自己的网站上。\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"ng-scope\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;line-height:1.2em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-top:0px;text-rendering:optimizelegibility;visibility:visible;max-width:620px;clear:both;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\tWISHTREND GLAM \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141439c8iDYaMPN7ghqW5H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这也是一个电商网站，你可以比较一下上面的这几家，看看有什么不同。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/04/best-korean-beauty-blogs-websites\" target=\"_blank\"><em>fashionista</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}